This is from my own frustration to not be able to find a good resource to learn the best foods in the places I visit. So, I am starting this as an experimentation. Please help me and other nomads to enjoy the best food in your country when traveling there. Let us know what's special in your place.

Use this format to comment--> Country: Food: Taste: Veg/non-veg:

Add as many food as you wish. Feel free to add more details if necessary. Thank you.
